1691       // additional broadcasts. No extra broadcasts are needed, if either only
1692       // the scalars of the recipe are used, or at least one of the operands
1693       // would require a broadcast. In the latter case, the single-scalar may
1694       // need to be broadcasted, but another broadcast is removed.
